title: Centered Landmines Renew
descriptionMarkdown:
The old "Centered landmines" blueprint by Goo se doesn't align to the center of the tile in Factorio version 1.0. So I changed the JSON code a little bit using "Factorio 0.15 blueprints decoder/encoder" to make it work like before and better. The blueprint can rotate and match with original landmines' positions exactly now.

References: \
"Centered landmines" by Goo se, https://factorioprints.com/view/-KtncLyCBZMDSz5Mjkez \
"Factorio 0.15 blueprints decoder/encoder", https://factorio.tmin10.ru/
